Class MapBackedPropertiesDelegate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.microbean.jersey.netty.MapBackedPropertiesDelegate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PropertiesDelegate

    public class MapBackedPropertiesDelegate
extends Object
implements PropertiesDelegate
    A simple PropertiesDelegate built around a Map.

    Thread Safety

    Instances of this class are not safe for concurrent use by multiple threads.

    Author:
    Laird Nelson

      • getPropertyNames

        public final Collection<String> getPropertyNames()
        Returns a Collection of the names of properties that this MapBackedPropertiesDelegate stores.

        This method never returns null.

        The order of the elements of the returned Collection is deliberately unspecified, is subject to change, and must not be relied upon.

        Specified by:
